description: Terrifically located 2 Bedroom with Spacious Living room, updated Kitchen and Bath, and a terrific Back deck& patio. Conveniently located on Upper East side, walkable to Seaport, Restaurants, Castle Island; this unit offers city living conveniences but on a quiet street. It's all about the VALUE here! The efficient layout takes advantage of its generous footprint and maximizes the space. Step into a spacious and well-lit living room featuring gas fireplace, recessed lighting, and in-ceiling speakers. The dine-in Kitchen boasts ample cabinetry, granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances. Walkout to the private rear deck that extends to a great patio, perfect for summer entertaining. The two well sized bedrooms each has proper closets and ceiling fans, serviced by a full bath. Centrally Heated and Cooled, with In-Building Laundry, and Low Condo Fees, this is a great starter home to build equity and enjoy the best of Southie & Seaport!
